1. *Njihovi* sinovi su veoma talentovani. (Their sons are very talented.)
2. Ovi ljudi su *njihovi* prijatelji. (These people are their friends.)
3. *Njihova* ponuda je veoma interesantna. (Their offer is very interesting.)
4. Oni su uzeli *njihov* novac. (They took their money.)
5. *Njihovim* prisustvom je ova večera postala zanimljivija. (Their presence made this evening more interesting.)
6. Ovo je *njihova* kuća. (This is their house.)
7. Oni su odgovorni za sve *njihove* greške. (They are responsible for all their mistakes.)